 <#
.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script ensures the System event log size is configured to 32768 KB or greater.
.NOTES
    Author          : Enioluwa Akinwande
    LinkedIn        : https://www.linkedin.com/in/enioluwa-akinwande-a5b597254/
